Package: kalinka-web
Version: @VERSION@
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Enhances: kalinka-server
Maintainer: Dmitry Savin <envelsavinds@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://kalinkaplayer.com
Description: Kalinka web remote (browser player UI)
 Browser-based remote control for the Kalinka music server. Installs the
 player web app where the server serves it: open http://<host>:<port> (the
 server's own address) in a browser on your network and control playback.
 .
 Install this on the same machine as kalinka-server. The bundle is
 architecture-independent, so this single package works on every platform the
 server supports.
